    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前《息风谷战略》的开发正处于全力冲刺阶段，以下是游戏在正式发售之前我们的开发及更新计划，有请各位掌门过目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>另外重要的事情说三遍：不EA，不EA，不EA！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/9ae05ffe7c3b664b8c2f5418f40527b5.avif?t=1771906136\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras_big/9ae05ffe7c3b664b8c2f5418f40527b5.avif?t=1771906136 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>支持MOD编辑器与内置创意工坊！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现已登陆DEMO免费试玩，参与MOD制作及测试即有机会赢得丰厚奖励！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们的精英共创QQ群：<strong><u>897933161</u></strong>，开发手把手教学！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抢先试玩游戏版本，获取第一手游戏进度咨询，成为《息风谷战略》<strong>的元老MOD作者</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/3f49a6338724d13270081a6d0111f054.poster.avif?t=1771906136\" width=600 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/3f49a6338724d13270081a6d0111f054.webm?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/3f49a6338724d13270081a6d0111f054.mp4?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场突如其来的灭门惨案，彻底颠覆了你——虎焰门少主<strong>司徒来也</strong>原本波澜不惊的人生。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为虎焰门的<strong>新晋掌门</strong>，临危受命的你是否能扶大厦之将倾，挽狂澜于既倒？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >息风谷风云骤变、狼烟四起，初入江湖的你是否能在多方势力的层层包围下觅得<strong>破局之道</strong>？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >名为<strong>“夜鸦”</strong>的凶兽传说甚嚣尘上，肩负血海深仇的你又是否能拨开重重迷雾，揪出真正的幕后黑手？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/1c79d1b12869310191da582b420f0d82.poster.avif?t=1771906136\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/1c79d1b12869310191da582b420f0d82.webm?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/1c79d1b12869310191da582b420f0d82.mp4?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《息风谷战略》采用经典的<strong>地域压制</strong>作为策略环节的核心玩法， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时还融合了大量围绕门派展开的<strong>经营模拟</strong>要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要合理利用手上的资源，在已方回合中慎重思考每一次行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发展据点，招贤纳士；分析形势，部署战略；进攻退守，步步为营……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以虎焰堂为起点，征服息风谷的各大门派吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/295ca589c80dff22b356a91d0fc43d86.poster.avif?t=1771906136\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/295ca589c80dff22b356a91d0fc43d86.webm?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/295ca589c80dff22b356a91d0fc43d86.mp4?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上兵伐谋，其次伐交。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正所谓“天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。” </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >群雄逐鹿于江湖，利益之下，从无“绝对”二字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以大敌当前，是战是和？危难之际，究竟谁才是值得信任的盟友？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >息风谷形势瞬息万变，唯有洞悉一切之人，方能立足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/b06782eaace87e6b49658a78bfe098f0.poster.avif?t=1771906136\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/b06782eaace87e6b49658a78bfe098f0.webm?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/b06782eaace87e6b49658a78bfe098f0.mp4?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《息风谷战略》的战斗环节将以<strong>“强调战前部署的类自走棋”</strong>的模式呈现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家既可以通过手动释放技能从而在战斗抢占先机，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也能借由指令系统提前为角色下达详细的战术安排。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富且多变的战斗系统将为你提供充足的策略性与可玩性。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有角色都拥有自己独立的<strong>成长系统</strong>，以及自身战斗风格所赋予的长短板。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >养成方向的不同，将在很大程度上决定他们所能在门派斗争中发挥的作用。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还请牢牢记住，唯有合理的<strong>角色Build</strong>与<strong>阵容组合</strong>才是让团队克敌制胜的不二法门！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/dae113a75d0fa328a8e5537fb0a0c57e.poster.avif?t=1771906136\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/dae113a75d0fa328a8e5537fb0a0c57e.webm?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/dae113a75d0fa328a8e5537fb0a0c57e.mp4?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >危险与机遇，阴谋与背叛，仇恨与羁绊，爱情与友情...... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自你决意迈入江湖的那一刻起，冥冥之中，一切命数好似已然注定。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明暗交织、错综复杂的庞大剧本，跌宕起伏、悬念迭生的故事情节，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将带你一同探寻息风谷各大门派之间尘封数十年的<strong>恩怨情仇</strong>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/28e9e74205aed70eb083343ab430c15f.poster.avif?t=1771906136\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/28e9e74205aed70eb083343ab430c15f.webm?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/28e9e74205aed70eb083343ab430c15f.mp4?t=1771906136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了门派之间的尔虞我诈、日夜攻伐？也许是时候开启一场真正的冒险了！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了围绕大地图展开的策略经营玩法外，《息风谷战略》还为玩家准备了许多可供游玩的特殊<strong>副本</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从机关密布的远古遗迹，到人迹罕至的静谧山谷，再到贼人盘踞的凶险之地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在深入探索这些副本的过程中你将体验到独特的剧情及战斗，并收获丰富的<strong>战利品奖励</strong>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206520/extras/98459d58b2492a62929f986b1cb10ebf.avif?t=1771906136\" width=640 height=140 /></span></p>",
